reviews.review_text: Not a very good AUD you can get better AUD's from this Warfield run.  Avoid this one.

Warfield's tough I was never a big fan of Warfield AUDs.  This is a good recording of what sounds like a difficult acoustic setting.

I'm going to amend my rating up to four stars, since my ear's developed a bit since I first wrote this.  Listening to it again, the acoustics sound very similar to the Capitol Theatre in Port Chester, NY.  This could be one of the Ken and Judy tapes.  So wtf, five stars. :-)  Great show, download it. :-)

Damn, the jam in TOO right before the second verse SMOKES!!!!

Encore It sounds just fine to me, people are WAY to picky.  Was filling in gaps of missing shows/and or songs.  I have the show, but was missing encoure, so now I was able to get my misssing U.S. Blues----and it sounds great to me.

Just like being there... ...loud guy announcing what each song is included!

Super duper AUD.

-q
